data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!! Fantastic opportunity to own a brick-front townhome located in the sought after Potomac Station neighborhood of Leesburg, Virginia. Conveniently situated just minutes away from Route 7, the toll road, Giant, Wegman’s, Village at Leesburg, downtown historic Leesburg, Leesburg Outlets, Bolden athletic fields, and Dulles Airport. The main floor of this home welcomes you with an open floor plan, gleaming hardwood floors, neutral paint throughout, and an abundance of natural light. The eat-in kitchen boasts granite countertops, a breakfast bar, table space, stainless steel appliances, and a pantry. Upstairs, you'll find the owner's suite with vaulted ceilings, a walk-in closet featuring custom cabinetry, and an en-suite bath with dual sinks. Down the hallway you’ll find the second bedroom complete with a custom closet and private bath. The fully finished lower level features a bonus room with walk-in closet and full bathroom that can serve as a guest room, craft room, or office...the possibilities are endless! The level is completed with a living area, cozy gas fireplace, and walkout to a fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or relaxing in the comfort of your own home. Notable updates include a new roof (2017), new washer and dryer (2022), new stainless steel appliances (2022), new carpet and paint (2022).
